OL,4,G2330FMurdered At First Sight
OL,5,     GOn July 4, 2017 Jorge Rodriguez
OL,6,     Gis shot while buying tomatoes for
OL,7,     Ga family event in Washington. He
OL,8,     Gdies seeking help. Days later, 17-
OL,9,     Gyear-old Pedro Cardenas is
OL,10,     Garrested after a tip-off.
OL,11,G0030FMy Lover, My Killer
